Compared to our work both papers aim to provide the means for  protecting the integrity and confidentiality of messages whereas the goal for our work is to enforce access control inside the  broker network.
While the work concentrated on using scopes as mechanism for structuring large-scale event-based systems, the notion of event visibility does resonate with access  control to some extent. 
The contributions of Srivatsa et al.
